hadiths[25]{hadithnumber,text}:
2133,"(eik din ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamari taraf nikley, us waqt hum sab taqdir key masley mein behes o mubaahasa kar rahey they, aap ghussa ho gaey yahan tak ke aap ka chehra surkh ho gaya aur aisa nazar aaney laga goya aap key گالوں par anaar key daney nichod diye gaey hon . aap ney farmaya : '' kya tumhen usi ka hukm diya gaya hai, ya mein usi wastey tumhari taraf Nabi bana kar bheja gaya hun? beshak tum sey pehli ummaten halak ho gaeen jab unhoney us masley mein behes o mubaahasa kya, main tumhen qism dilata hun ke us masley mein behes o mubaahasa na karo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey is sanad sey sirf Saleh miri ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Saleh miri key bahut sarey gharaaib hain jinki riwayat mein wo munfarid hain, koi unki mutaabiat nahin karta 3- is bab mein umr , Aaisha aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2134,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Adam aur Musa ney baham (aapas mein) munazara kya, Musa ney kaha : Adam! aap wohi to hain jisey Allah Taala ney apney haath sey paida kya aur aap key andar apni rooh phunki padhi. phir aap ney logon ko gumrah kya aur in ko jannat sey nikala ? Adam ney uskey jawab mein kaha : aap wohi Musa hain jisey Allah Taala ney guftgu karney key liye muntakhab kya, kya aap merey aisey kaam par mujhey malamat kartey hain jisey Allah Taala ney aasman o zamin ko paida karney sey pehley merey ooper lazim kar diya tha? Adam Musa sey daleel mein jeet gaey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- ye hadees is sanad sey yani Suleman (Alaihissalam) taimi ki riwayat sey jisey wo Aamash sey riwayat kartey hain, 3- Aamash key baaz shagirdon ney « an Aamash an abi Saleh an abi Hurera an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai. aur baaz ney iski sanad yun bayan ki hai « an Aamash an abi Saleh an abi Saeed an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » , padhi. 4- kaee aur sanadon sey ye hadees Abu-Hurera key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai, 5- is bab mein umr aur Jundub Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2135,"unhoney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! jo amal hum kartey hain uskey barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai, wo naya shuru honey wala Amr hai ya aisa Amr hai jis sey faraaghat ho chuki hai? padhi. aap ney farmaya : '' ibn khattab ! wo aisa Amr hai jis sey faraaghat ho chuki hai, aur har aadmi key liye wo Amr aasan kar diya gaya hai) jis key liye wo paida kya gaya hai) , chunanche jo aadmi sa'adat mandon mein sey hai wo sa'adat wala kaam karta hai aur jo bad-bakhton mein sey hai wo bad-bakhti wala kaam karta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Huzefa bin Usaid , Anas aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2136,"hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas bethey huye they, aap zamin kured rahey they ke achcha aap ney aasman ki taraf apna sar uthaya phir farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi aadmi aisa nahin hai jis ka haal malum na ho, ( Wakee ki riwayat mein hai : tum mein sey koi aadmi aisa nahin jiski jannat ya jahannam ki jagah na likh di gaee ho ( , Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum log ( taqdir key likhey huye par) bharosa na kar lein ? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin, tum log amal karo isliye ke har aadmi key liye wo chiz aasan kar di gaee hai jis key liye wo paida kya gaya hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2137,"hum sey saadiq o masdooq Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bayan kya, ''tum mein sey har aadmi apni maa key pet mein chaalis din tak nutfey ki shakal mein rehta hai, phir itney hi din tak jamey huye khoon (alqa) ki shakal mein rehta hai, phir itney hi din tak « مضغة » (yani gosht key lothdey) ki shakal mein rehta hai, phir Allah Taala uskey paas farishta bhejna hai jo uskey andar rooh phoonktaa hai, phir usey chaar chizon ( key likhney (ka hukm kya jata hai, chunanche wo likhta hai : uska rizq , uski maut , uska amal aur ye chiz ke wo « شقي » ( bad-bakht ( hai ya « Saeed » ( nek bakht ( , us zaat ki qism jis key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, tum mein sey koi aadmi jannatiyon ka amal karta rehta hai yahan tak ke uskey aur jannat key darmiyan eik gaz ka fasla reh jata hai phir uskey ooper likhi hui taqdir ghalib aati hai aur jahannamiyon key amal par uska khatima kya jata hai. lihaza wo jahannam mein dakhil ho jata hai, aur tum mein sey koi aadmi jahannamiyon ka amal karta rehta hai phir uskey ooper likhi hui taqdir ghalib aati hai aur jannatiyon key amal par uska khatima kya jata hai, lihaza wo jannat mein dakhil hota hai."
2138,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har bacha fitrat ( Islam ( par paida hota hai padhi. , phir uskey maa baap usey Yahudi , nasrani , ya mushrik banatey hain'' arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! jo is sey pehley hi mar jaey ? padhi. aap ney farmaya : '' Allah khub janta hai ke wo kya amal kartey ''."
2139,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' dua key siwa koi chiz taqdir ko nahin taalti hai padhi. aur neki key siwa koi chiz umr mein izafa nahin karti hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Salman ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Usaid sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- hum isey sirf Yahya bin Zures ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 4- Abu-Modud do raawiyon ki kunniyat hai, eik ko Fiza kaha jata hai, aur ye wohi hain jinhoney ye hadees riwayat ki hai, unka naam Fizza hai aur doosrey Abu-Modud ka naam abdul-Azeez bin Abu-Suleman hai, un mein sey eik Basra key rehney waley hain aur doosrey Madina key , dono eik hi daur mein they."
2140,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aksar ye dua padhtey they یا مقلب القلوب ثبت قلبِ على دینك '' aey dilon key ulatney palatney waley merey dil ko apney Deen par Sabit rakh'', mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! hum log aap par aur aap ki laai hui shariyat par eman ley aaye kya aap ko hamarey silsiley mein andesha rehta hai? aap ney farmaya : '' haan , logon key dil Allah ki ungliyon mein sey do ungliyon key darmiyan hain jaisa chahta hai unhen ulat'ta-palat'ta rehta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- kaee logon ney usi tarah (عن الأعمش an أبي سفيان an أنس) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai. baaz logon ney (عن الأعمش an أبي سفيان an جابر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai, lekin abu-Sufiyaan ki hadees jo Anas sey marvi hai ziyada sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein nawaas bin Samaan , Umme-Salma , Abdullah bin Amr aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2141,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (eik baar ( hamari taraf nikley us waqt aap key haath mein do kitaben thin . aap ney puchha : '' tum log jantey ho ye dono kitaben kya hain? '' hum logon ney kaha : nahin, siwaye iskey ke aap hamen bata den . dahiney haath wali kitab key barey mein aap ney farmaya : '' ye rabbul-aalameen ki kitab hai, uskey andar jannatiyon , unkey aaba o ijdaad aur unkey qabeelon key naam hain, phir aakhir mein unka meezaan zikr kar diya gaya hai. lihaza un mein na to kisi ka izafa hoga aur na un mein sey koi kam hoga '' , phir aap ney baaein hath wali kitab key barey mein farmaya : ''ye rabbul-aalameen ki kitab hai, uskey andar jahannamiyon, unkey aaba o ijdad aur unkey qabeelon key naam hain aur aakhir mein unka meezaan zikr kar diya gaya hai, ab un mein na to kisi ka izafa hoga aur na un mein sey koi kam hoga. Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! phir amal kis liye karen jabke us mamley sey faraaghat ho chuki hai? aap ney farmaya : '' sidhi raah par chalo aur miyaana rawi ikhtiyar karo, isliye ke jannati ka khatima jannati key amal pe hoga, agar-che is sey pehley wo jo bhi amal karey aur jahannami ka khatima jahannami key amal pe hoga agar-che is sey pehley wo jo bhi amal kerey'', phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney dono haathon sey ishara kya, phir un dono kitabon ko phenk diya aur farmaya : '' tumhara rab bandon sey farigh ho chuka hai, eik fariq jannat mein jaeyga aur eik fariq jahannam mein jaeyga ''."
2142,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah Taala kisi bandey key sath bhalai ka irada karta hai to us sey amal karata hai'', arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool! kaisey amal karata hai? aap ney farmaya : '' maut sey pehley usey amale-saleh ki tofiq deta hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2143,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey darmiyan khadey huye aur farmaya : '' kisi ki bimari doosrey ko nahin lagti '' , eik Erabi (dehati) (badwi) ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! khujli waley oont sey (jab usey badey mein latey hain) to tamam oont (khujli waley (ho jatey hain'' , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''phir pehley ko kis ney khujli di? kisi ki bimari doosrey ko nahin lagti hai aur na maah safar ki nahusat ki koi haqiqat hai, Allah Taala ney har nafs ko paida kya hai aur uski zindagi, rizq aur musibaton ko likh diya hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein abu-Huraira, ibne-Abbas aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2144,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi banda momin nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke achi aur buri taqdir par eman ley aaye, aur ye yaqin kar ley ke jo kuch usey laahiq huwa hai chookney wala na tha aur jo kuch chook gaya hai usey laahiq honey wala na tha''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdullah bin Memun ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Abdullah bin Memun munkire-hadees hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Ubada, Jabir aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2145,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi banda chaar chizon par eman laye baghair momin nahin ho sakta : (1) gawahi dey ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur main Allah ka Rasool hun, usney mujhey haq key sath bheja hai, (2) maut par eman laye, (3) marney key baad dobara uthaey janey par eman laye, (4-) taqdir par eman laye ''."
2146,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab Allah Taala kisi bandey ki maut key liye kisi zamin ka faisla kar deta hai to wahan uski koi hajat o zarurat paida kar deta hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- matar bin Ukamis ki Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is hadees key ilawa koi dusri hadees nahin malum hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Abu-Azza sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2147,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah Taala kisi bandey ki maut key liye kisi zamin ka faisla kar deta hai to wahan uski koi hajat paida kar deta hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- Abu Azza ko sharfe-sohbat hasil hai aur unka naam Yasar bin Abd hai, 3- Raavi abu-Mulaih ka naam Aamir bin Usama bin Umer hazli hai. unhen Zaid bin Usama bhi kaha jata hai."
2148,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aadmi ney aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool! ye dam jin sey hum jhaad phunk kartey hain, dawaaein jinsey ilaj kartey hain aur bachaaw ki cheezen jin sey bachaaw kartey hain, aap bataiye kya ye Allah ki taqdir mein sey kuch lota sakti hain? aap ney farmaya : ''ye sab bhi to Allah ki taqdir sey hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : hum is hadees ko sirf Zohri ki riwayat sey jantey hain, kaee logon ney ye hadees (عن سفيان an الزهري an أبي خزامة an أبيه) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai, ye ziyada sahih hai. isi tarah kaee logon ney (عن الزهري an أبي خزامة an أبيه) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai."
2149,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat key do qism key logon key liye Islam mein koi hissa nahin hai : (1) Marjiya (2 ( Qadriya'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Umar, ibne-Umar aur Raafey bin khadeej (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2150,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ibne-Adam ki misal aisi hai ke uskey pehlu mein ninnanwey aafatein hain agar wo un aafaton sey bach gaya to budhapey mein giraftar ho jaeyga yahan tak ke usey maut aa jaeygi'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain.
2151,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah key faisley par razi hona ibne-Adam ki sa'adat ( nek bakhti ( hai, Allah sey khair talab na karna ibne-Adam ki shaqaawat ( bad-bakhti ( hai aur Allah key faisley par naraz hona ibne-Adam ki shaqaawat (bad-bakhti) hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Muhammad bin abi Humed ki riwayat sey jantey hain, unhen Hammad bin abi Humed bhi kaha jata hai, unki kunniyat Abu-Ibrahim hai, aur Madina key rehney waley hain, ye muhaddeseen key nazdik qawi nahin hain."
2152,"ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key paas eik shakhs aaya aur usney kaha : falan shakhs ney aap ko salam arz kya hai, us sey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : mujhey khabar mili hai ke usney Deen mein naya aqeeda ejaad kya hai, agar usney Deen mein naya aqeeda ejaad kya hai to usey mera salam na pahunchana , isliye ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' is ummat mein ya meri ummat mein , ( ye shak Raavi ki taraf sey huwa hai) taqdir ka inkar karney walon par « khasaf » , padhi. « maskh » ya « qazaf » ka azab hoga '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- Abu-Sakhar ka naam Humed bin Ziyad hai."
2153,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat mein « khasaf » aur « maskh » ka azab hoga aur ye azab taqdir key jhutlaney walon par aayega ''.
2154,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' chhe qism key log aisey hain jin par mainey, Allah Taala ney aur tamam anbiya ney lanat bheji hai : Allah ki kitab mein izafa karney wala, Allah ki taqdir ko jhutlaney wala , taqat key zariey ghalba hasil karney wala, taake uskey zariey usey izzat dey jisey Allah ney zaleel kya hai, aur usey zaleel karey jisey Allah ney izzat bakhshi hai, Allah ki mohramaat ko halal samajhney wala , merey kunbey mein sey Allah ki mohramat ko halal samajhney wala aur meri sunnat tarak karney wala''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Mawali ney ye hadees isi tarah عن عبيد الله ابن عبدالرحمٰن بن موهب an عمرة an عائشة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai. Sufiyan Sory , Hafs bin Ghiyas aur kaee logon ney isey (عن عبيد الله بن عبدالرحمٰن بن موهب an علي بن حسين an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey mursalan riwayat kya hai. ye ziyada sahih hai."
2155,"main Makka gaya to Ata bin abi Ribah sey mulaqat ki aur un sey kaha : abu Muhammad ! Basra waley taqdir key silsiley mein (bar-sabile-inkar ( kuch guftgu kartey hain, unhoney kaha : betey! kya tum Quran padhtey ho? mainey kaha : haan, unhoney kaha : Sura Zukhruf padho, mainey padha : حم والكتاب المبين إنا جعلناه قرآنا عربيا لعلكم تعقلون وإنه في أم الكتاب لدينا لعلي حكيم '' Ha-Mim, qism hai is wazeh kitab ki, hamney isko Arbi zaban ka Quran banaya hai ke tum samajh lo, yaqinan ye loh (takhti) mehfooz mein hai, aur hamarey nazdik buland martaba hikmat wali hai'' ( Zukhruf 1-4) padhi , unhoney kaha : jantey ho Ummul-kitab kya hai? mainey kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain, unhoney kaha : wo eik kitab hai jisey Allah Taala ney aasman aur zamin key paida karney sey pehley likha hai, is mein ye likha huwa hai ke Firon jahannami hai aur us mein (تبت يدا أبي لهب وتب) '' Abu-Lahab key dono haath toot gaey, aur wo ( khud ( halak ho gaya '' ( تبت : padhi. ( bhi likha huwa hai. Ata kehtey hain : phir main Waleed bin Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila ( Waleed key walid Ubada bin Samit Sabab Rasool they (aur un sey sawal kya : martey waqt aap key walid ki kya wasiyat thi ? kaha : merey walid ney mujhey bulaya aur kaha : betey ! Allah sey daro aur ye jaan lo ke tum Allah sey hergiz nahin dar saktey jab tak tum Allah par aur taqdir ki achai aur burai par eman na laao, agar iskey siwa doosrey aqeeda par tumhari maut aayegi to jahannam mein jaaogey, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' Allah Taala ney sab sey pehley qalam ko paida kya '' aur farmaya : '' likho '' , qalam ney arz kya : kya likhun? Allah Taala ney farmaya : '' taqdir likho jo kuch ho chuka hai aur jo hamesha tak honey wala hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai."
2156,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''Allah taala ney taqdir ko zamin o aasman ki paidaish sey pachas hazar saal pehley likha tha''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
2157,"mushrekine-Quraish taqdir key barey mein jhagadtey huye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye to ye aayat nazil hui يوم يسحبون في النار على وجوههم ذوقوا مس سقر إنا كل شيء خلقناه بقدر yani ''jis din wo jahannam mein munh key bal ghasitey jaeyngey (to un sey kaha jaeyga) tum log jahannam ka maza chakho , hamney har chiz ko andazey sey paida kya hai'' (Qamar 48, 49) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- mazkura hadees mujh sey Qabisa ney bayan ki, wo kehtey hain : mujh sey Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid ney bayan ki."
